text: The End is the thirteenth and last book in the series A Series of Unfortunate Events by Lemony Snicket. The book was released on Friday, October 13, 2006. It reveals many secrets including the real meaning of V.F.D.; the secret organisation. It tells what is hidden in the famous Sugar Bowl. == References == Category:A Series of Unfortunate Events Category:2006 books
